###
### ❌ ERREUR: Moins de 3 compétences (minimum requis)
###
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profile/step/3
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "skills": [
    {
      "name": "React",
      "category": "frontend",
      "level": "intermediate"
    }
  ]
}

###
### ❌ ERREUR: Dates incohérentes (fin avant début)
###
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profile/step/4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "experiences": [
    {
      "title": "Developer",
      "company": "Company",
      "location": "Tunis",
      "startDate": "2023-12-31",
      "endDate": "2023-01-01",
      "description": "Invalid date range"
    }
  ]
}

###
### ❌ ERREUR: Utilisateur trop jeune (moins de 18 ans)
###
POST {{baseUrl}}/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "step1": {
    "firstName": "Young",
    "lastName": "Person",
    "phone": "+21625123456",
    "country": "Tunisia",
    "city": "Tunis",
    "dateOfBirth": "2010-05-15",
    "gender": "male",
    "email": "young@example.com",
    "address": "123 Rue Test",
    "zipCode": "1001"
  }
}

###
### ========== NOTES ==========
### 
### 1. Remplacez {{token}} par votre vrai token JWT
### 2. Phone: doit être un numéro tunisien valide +216
###    Format valide: /^(?:\+216|00216|0)?[245679]\d{7,8}$/
###    Exemples valides:
###    - +21625123456
###    - +21698765432
###    - 00216 25 123 456
###    - 0 25 123 456
### 3. Dates: format ISO (YYYY-MM-DD)
### 4. Âge minimum: 18 ans
### 5. Compétences: minimum 3 requises
### 
### ========== FLUX RECOMMANDÉ ==========
### 
### 1. POST /profile (step1)
###    ↓
### 2. PUT /profile/step/2 (éducation)
###    ↓
### 3. PUT /profile/step/3 (compétences) - min 3
###    ↓
### 4. PUT /profile/step/4 (expériences)
###    ↓
### 5. PUT /profile/step/5 (projets)
###    ↓
### 6. PUT /profile/step/6 (langues)
###    ↓
### 7. PUT /profile/step/7 (certifications)
###    ↓
### 8. PUT /profile/step/8 (profil cible - ÉTAPE FINALE)
###    ↓
### 9. GET /profile (voir résultat final)
###    ↓
### 10. GET /profile/summary (voir score et statistiques)
###
### ========== VALIDATION RULES ==========
###
### Step 1 (Personal Info):
###   - Age: minimum 18 years
###   - Phone: Tunisian number only (+216, 00216, or 0 prefix)
###   - Email: valid format
###
### Step 3 (Skills):
###   - Minimum 3 skills required
###   - No duplicate skills
###   - Levels: beginner, intermediate, advanced, expert
###
### Step 4 (Experiences):
###   - End date must be >= start date
###   - Description required
###
### Step 8 (Target Profile):
###   - Salary: minSalary < maxSalary
###   - Remote type: if "hybrid", hybridDays required (1-5)
###   - Availability: must be valid enum
###   - All fields are optional (entirely skippable step)
###
